duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide nutrition counseling, care plans, assessment, and education programs for diverse population
Assess nutritional needs, complete nutritional plans, and screen patients for nutritional risk
Complete diet and food drug interaction instructions and attend Care Conferences to address patient’s nutritional needs
Document nutritional needs of high-risk patients in a timely manner including holidays and weekends
Maintain privacy and confidentiality at all times and participate in mandatory in-service meetings

education_certification.credential: Registered Dietitian license in the state of Ohio
Knowledge of food preparation, food safety, and sanitation practices
Prior experience teaching and counseling nutrition therapy
